To activate openrc, please add the following into /etc/rc.conf:

openrc_enable="YES"

Or set the following in /boot/loader.conf for it to completly take over rc:

init_path="/usr/local/sbin/init"

Init scripts are to be installed at:

/usr/local/etc/init.d/

Configuration for init scripts are to be installed at:

/usr/local/etc/conf.d/

Add scripts to runlevels:

rc-update add zfs boot
rc-update add zvol boot

Start, stop, or restart services:

rc-service zfs start
rc-service zfs stop
rc-service zfs restart
